You know,

5
00:00:12,610 --> 00:00:14,370
the Chinese Communist Party is a little like...

6
00:00:14,370 --> 00:00:15,370
Smaug!

7
00:00:15,370 --> 00:00:17,300
Sure, it seems big and scary.

8
00:00:17,300 --> 00:00:19,869
But then it starts to show off…

9
00:00:19,869 --> 00:00:22,949
My teeth swords.

10
